<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM1.8.3">
<l>pañcavar tūtaṉāyp pārataṅ kaiceytu</l>
<l>nañcumiḻ nākaṅ kiṭantanaṟ poykaipuk</l>
<l>kañcap paṇattiṉmēṟ pāyntiṭ ṭaruṭceyta</l>
<l>vañcaṉa vaṇṇaṉē yaccō vaccō</l>
<l rend="indent">vāyar perumāṉē yaccō vaccō</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>He with the black complexion who,</l>
<l>having assisted in the Bhārata [war]</l>
<l rend="indent">as the messenger of the five [Pāṇḍavas],</l>
<l>entered the good pond where the serpent that spit poison reclined,</l>
<l>[and] graciously lept on the hood of the cobra</l>
<l rend="indent">so that [it] feared [him]! Oh! Oh!</l>
<l>Lord of the Cowherds, Oh! Oh!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
